snippet: Iraqi security forces killed 11 people suspected of being militants and arrested dozens of others in a large military-led operation north of Baghdad on Monday, military officials said.
abstract: Iraqi security forces kill 11 people suspected of being militants and arrest dozens of others in large military-led operation north of Baghdad.
